								<p class="scope field"><b>BUSINESS CHALLENGE:</b> To prepare for the audits carried out by the security group from headquarters so as to have more room for maneuver to remedy the vulnerabilities and comply with the commitments made by the French Group’s CIO and Managing Director.</p>
								<p class="size field"><b>SOLUTION:</b>
									<ul class="solutions">
