				<h2 class="heading--2">An external perspective on vulnerabilities</h2>

				<p class="paragraph--2"><b><i>“We already had open source vulnerability analysis tools but few industrialized and formalized procedures. Moreover, they were used by the same team that operates IT production, which were therefore both judge and party. We were therefore looking for a SaaS solution in order to have an external overview of our security posture from an outside party!”</i></b> explains Lauriat.</p>

				<p class="paragraph--2">When we were looking at the products on the market, we found that the Qualys solution stood out for very pragmatic reasons. <b><i>“It was a de facto choice since it is already the solution used by our headquarters to assess us.</i></b></p>
			</div>
